dict.string: 'SuccessEntellus' app needs access to allow adding events to your calendar.
'SuccessEntellus' app needs access to allow camera to capture image for your profile picture and business image.

'SuccessEntellus' app needs access to your device contacts in order to upload them to the server so that they can be easily imported/exported in future. For our privacy policy, please go to help section.

'SuccessEntellus' app needs access to your current location to connect you with CFTs near you. If you are a CFT, then your current location will be tracked. We suggest always allowing for best optimal experience and maximum sales leads.
